quite 
&gt; astronomical of that being coincidence. Same goes for any of us asking a question, any 
&gt; question, and receiving a relevant response ... it would be highly unlikely for it to be 
from 
&gt; stray signals (of whatever flavor.) 
&gt; 
&gt; Then again, if he has trouble even hearing and/or agreeing on the content, it&#39;s going to 
be 
